    <div class="active" id="showproduct">
      <h1 class='title' align="center">金石相契·尊汉堂金石碑帖特展</h1>
      

<script src="/Templates/cn2014/js/ShopShow.js"></script>
      <div style="clear:both;"></div>
      <div class="editor" id="metbox">
        <div class="box" >
          <div><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 28px"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 19px; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri">&nbsp;<img src="/upLoad/product/month_1612/201612292218187631.jpg"/></span></span></p><p style="BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-ALIGN: justify; TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 37px"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 19px; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; COLOR: rgb(62,62,62); LINE-HEIGHT: 150%">古墨文章</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 19px; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; COLOR: rgb(62,62,62); LINE-HEIGHT: 150%">, </span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 19px; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; COLOR: rgb(62,62,62); LINE-HEIGHT: 150%">不离金石，金石相契，椎拓载道。</span></span></p><p style="BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-ALIGN: justify; TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 37px"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 19px; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; COLOR: rgb(62,62,62); LINE-HEIGHT: 150%">中华传统文化博大精深，千百年来儒、释、道精神是古人追求的最高境界，金石文化是这座金字塔的精华所在，而金石碑帖作为重要载体之一，</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 19px; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%">集书法、文字、史料价值于一身，</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 19px; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; COLOR: rgb(62,62,62); LINE-HEIGHT: 150%">具有考古正史、订误证伪、传承发扬的重要意义。潍坊自古为金石重镇，以陈介祺为代表的金石大家，以收藏、研究、传拓、考据而名镇海内，为金石文化的传承和发扬打下了坚实基础。</span></span></p><p style="BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-ALIGN: justify; TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 37px"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 19px; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; COLOR: rgb(62,62,62); LINE-HEIGHT: 150%">此次特展是潍坊市博物馆有史以来规模最大的一次金石碑拓展览，全部藏品由尊汉堂堂主张志亮先生提供。张志亮先生为山东安丘人，参军退伍后居住洛阳，工作之余收藏和研究金石拓本，共藏有周秦、汉唐直至民国以来的重要金石碑帖千余件，多系民国之前旧拓。回到家乡举办展览，张先生是怀着对学术的敬畏之心与对家乡的感恩之情，也是二十多年来对金石文字学习的一次重要汇报。展览展出的藏品为精品中的精品，均为中国书法史上的名碑巨帖，内容之精、存世之少、涉及年代之早，可谓是收藏界所稀见。与此同时，张志亮先生是传拓技艺非物质文化遗产传承人，尤擅青铜器全形拓，是青铜器全形拓大家周佩珠先生的弟子，继承了故宫博物院马子云先生的余脉，使传拓技艺后继有人，传承有序。</span></span></p><p style="BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-ALIGN: justify; TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 37px"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 19px; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; COLOR: rgb(62,62,62); LINE-HEIGHT: 150%">通过本次展览我们也充分感受到金石文字的魅力，在金石学重振的今天，古人留存的只字片纸亦是弥足珍贵，希望通过我们共同的努力，将中国的传统文化继承和发扬。</span></span></p><p style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 37px"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 19px; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 37px"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 19px; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri"></span></span></p><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 37px"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri"><img alt="14830211384228300.jpg" src="/upload/image/20161229/14830211384228300.jpg"/><span style="FONT-SIZE: 19px; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 43px"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri"><strong><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%">&nbsp;</span></strong><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%">&nbsp;&nbsp;《纪泰山铭》拓片</span></span></p><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri"><img alt="14830211458497038.jpg" src="/upload/image/20161229/14830211458497038.jpg"/></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 14px; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri">&nbsp;</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><script src="/inc/AspCms_VisitsAdd.asp?id=177"></script>
            <div id="metinfo_additional"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
